	<div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/05/05/morning-agenda-a-saturday-in-omaha/" data-title="Saturday With Buffett in Omaha" data-description="Warren E. Buffett fielded questions at Berkshire Hathawayâs annual meeting. | Wall Street banks are embracing a rule they once hated. | A Delaware judge upheld Sotheby&#039;s poison pill. | David Einhorn&#039;s hedge fund asked the S.E.C. to delay disclosures.">
